snippet: An embassy spokesman said that the victim, who was not affiliated with the embassy, was taken to a hospital, and that the attacker was arrested.
abstract: Egyptian man stabs American man outside United States Embassy in Cairo; reasons for stabbing remain unclear.
lead_paragraph: An embassy spokesman said that the victim, who was not affiliated with the embassy, was taken to a hospital, and that the attacker was arrested.

headline.seo: American Stabbed Outside U.S. Embassy in Cairo
headline.main: U.S. Man Is Stabbed at Embassy in Cairo
